large accumulation of mud. The noise from these vehicles destroys the peace and </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">tranquillity</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> too. More seriously unfortunately some vehicles are driven in an aggressive and dangerous manner which puts other users of these routes at risk of injury or worse (</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">walkers</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> cyclists and horse riders.)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I urge the committee to recommend legislation to exclude off road vehicles from these trails lanes etc in our National Parks and AONBs</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Angela Hilton</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Retired Consultant Chest Physician</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Chair Ramblers Trafford</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">2</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> September 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>